{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|ねこま}}

{{IPAfont|*⟨ni<sub>1</sub>a-ko<sub>1</sub>ma⟩}} → {{IPAfont|⟨ne<sub>1</sub>ko<sub>1</sub>ma⟩}} → {{IPAchar|/nekoma/}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|sort=ねこま|-}}.  Originally a compound of {{compound|ja|sort=ねこま|にゃ|tr1=nya|t1=[[onomatopoeia]] for the sound a cat makes (compare {{noncog|en|mew}}, [[meow]])|こま|tr2=koma|t2=four-legged animal}}.

Obsolete; replaced by shorter form ''neko'' in modern Japanese.

{{ja-noun|ねこま}}

